Natty or not content is pointless.

The logic is: 

If someone is natural, and I am natural, then I can realistically achieve their physique.

But if someone is enhanced, and I am natural, then I can‚Äôt realistically achieve their physique.

This is a fallacy though. Even if you‚Äôre both natural, you will never have the same genetics and you may never achieve the same physique.

The solution: only compare yourself to your starting place. Stop comparing yourself to others.
